name: CompressionQuality
shortdesc: The amount and type of compression to use for bitmap images.

property.name: MINIMUM
property.shortdesc: Uses minimum compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: LOW
property.shortdesc: Uses low compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: MEDIUM
property.shortdesc: Uses medium compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: HIGH
property.shortdesc: Uses high compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: MAXIMUM
property.shortdesc: Uses maximum compression. Not valid when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: FOUR_BIT
property.shortdesc: Uses 4-bit compression. Valid only when bitmap compression is ZIP.

property.name: EIGHT_BIT
property.shortdesc: Uses 8-bit compression. Valid only when bitmap compression is ZIP.
